    "text_kelimeler": "\"(1) Hikmetli.\n(2) Öğütten.\"",
    "text_okunus": "ẕâlike netlûhü `aleyke mine-l'âyâti veẕẕikri-lḥakîm."
  },
  {
    "ayet": 59,
